 by them to England, superseding the native Old English form, <i>Wealdhere</i>. It was a very popular name in medieval England, normally pronounced ‘Water’."],"variants":[{"name":"Walther","meanings":["from <i>wald</i> ‘rule’ + <i>heri</i> ‘army’; name of the famous medieval minnesinger  Walther von der Vogelweide  (  <i>c.</i>1170– <i>c.</i>1230 )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Walter de Cantilupe was born in 1107, in Canteleu, Seine-Maritime, Normandy, France, his father, Gilbert de Cantilupe, was 36 and his mother, Fern Wright, was 25. He had at least 1 son with Emecina de Cantilupe d'Oyrieres. He died in 1161, in Isles-sur-Suippe, Marne, Champagne-Ardenne, France, at the age of 54."},"et":{"1107–1161":"1107–1161","1105–1161":"1105–1161","1133–1204":"1133–1204","1071–1130":"1071–1130","1082–1163":"1082–1163","1107":"1107","about 1161":"umbes 1161","1204":"1204","1105":"1105","Abt 1133":"umbes 1133","1133":"1133","1130":"1130","1163":"1163","1161":"1161","1082":"1082","1071":"1071","Longueville, Jersey":"Longueville, Jersey saar","Clécy, Calvados, France":"Clécy, Calvados, Prantsusmaa","Canteleu, Normandy, France":"Canteleu, Seine-Maritime, Normandie, Prantsusmaa","Maine, Maine et Loir, Rhone-Alpes, France":"Rhône-Alpes, Prantsusmaa","Isles, Marne, Champagne-Ardenne, France":"Isles-sur-Suippe, Marne, Champagne-Ardenne, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"1107–1161":"1107–1161","1105–1161":"1105–1161","1133–1204":"1133–1204","1071–1130":"1071–1130","1082–1163":"1082–1163","1107":"1107","about 1161":"noin 1161","1204":"1204","1105":"1105","Abt 1133":"noin 1133","1133":"1133","1130":"1130","1163":"1163","1161":"1161","1082":"1082","1071":"1071","Longueville, Jersey":"Longueville, Jersey","Clécy, Calvados, France":"Clécy, Calvados, Ranska","Canteleu, Normandy, France":"Canteleu, Seine-Maritime, Normandie, Ranska","Maine, Maine et Loir, Rhone-Alpes, France":"Rhône-Alpes, Ranska","Isles, Marne, Champagne-Ardenne, France":"Isles-sur-Suippe, Marne, Champagne-Ardenne, Ranska"},"fr":{"1107–11